<item>
            <title>[CASSANDRA-915] disallow column family names containing hyphens</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-915</link>
                <project id="12310865" key="CASSANDRA">Apache Cassandra</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;You cannot use use hyphens in column family names because hyphens are used as delimiters in sstable filenames (which are derived from the CF name). &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;It should be an error to configure such a column family name.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
